SSH Plugin for qnotifier
==========================

1. Install the Net:SSH gem: `gem install net-ssh`

2. Enable the plugin in the qnotifier config.

3. Create a locked down user with a chroot. Then login as the same user you use to run qnotifier and copy your ssh key across e.g.: `ssh-copy-id lockeddownuser@localhost`   

4. Edit the file replacing <hostname> and <user> with your own (localhost, lockeddownuser)

5. Run qnotifier



